Rainbow Aura

The rainbow aura is a construction of druidic power
which protects the subject against elemental attacks:
fire, cold, lightning, and water.

(Note: You do not have to wear the rainbow object.
It protects you automatically.)

Command: rainbow <target> (defaults to caster)
Base Cost: 40 SP
Base Recovery: medium
Base Effect: protection (moderate)
Base Duration: medium-long
Guild Level: 4
